# `enrollDevice`

**Signature:** `fleetEnabled validMetadata authResult activationResult`

4.2 enrollDevice (activate)

| # | Condition | Result |
|---|-----------|--------|
| 1 | ~ fleetEnabled | [ER_Disabled](../types.md#enrollmentresult) |
| 2 | ~ validMetadata | [ER_Unauthorized](../types.md#enrollmentresult) |
| 3 | authResult == [AR_Authenticated](../types.md#authresult) |  |
| 4 | activationResult == [AC_Success](../types.md#activationresult) | [ER_Succeeded](../types.md#enrollmentresult) |
| 5 | activationResult == [AC_AlreadyActive](../types.md#activationresult) | [ER_Unauthorized](../types.md#enrollmentresult) |
| 6 | *(otherwise)* | [ER_InternalError](../types.md#enrollmentresult)) |
| 7 | authResult == [AR_VaultUnavailable](../types.md#authresult) | [ER_InternalError](../types.md#enrollmentresult) |
| 8 | *(otherwise)* | [ER_Unauthorized](../types.md#enrollmentresult) |

